{
  "texts": [
    "No mice were excluded from the analyses.",
    "For all assays, mice were euthanized with EUTHASOL™ (Virbac) and transcardially perfused with phosphate buffer saline, pH 7.4, at room temperature (RT).",
    "Experimenters were not blinded to the sample groups.",
    "For the cynomolgus macaque experiment (n = 1), the study plan involving the care and use of animals was reviewed and approved by the Charles River CR-LAV Institutional Animal and Use Committee (IACUC).",
    "During the study, the care and use of animals were conducted by CR-LAV with guidance from the USA National Research Council and the Canadian Council on Animal Care (CCAC)."
  ]
}